- id: gh-action
  subject: Write GitHub Actions workflow to build and deploy GH Pages
  status: pending
  description: Workflow that runs on push to main, installs deps, runs PurgeCSS on rippleui against docs/index.html, deploys docs/ to GH Pages for AnEntrypoint/floosie
  effort: small
  category: infra
  blocking: []
  blockedBy: []
  acceptance:
    - .github/workflows/gh-pages.yml exists
    - Workflow triggers on push to main
    - Installs Node deps, runs purgecss to generate docs/vendor/rippleui.css
    - Deploys docs/ directory to GH Pages
    - No secrets required beyond GITHUB_TOKEN
  edge_cases:
    - gh-pages deploy action must have write permissions

- id: add-remote
  subject: Add AnEntrypoint/floosie as push remote and push
  status: pending
  description: Add AnEntrypoint/floosie remote, commit all pending changes, push to main
  effort: small
  category: infra
  blocking: []
  blockedBy: ["gh-action"]
  acceptance:
    - git remote shows AnEntrypoint/floosie
    - all files committed and pushed
  edge_cases:
    - repo may already exist